One of Argentina 's top referees is under investigation and faces a possible ban after overturning a red card and penalty decision based on a television replay .
Referee German Delfino awarded a penalty to Velez Sarsfield after Daniel Valencia was adjudged to have handled the ball in the area and showed the Arsenal man his second booking of the game .
However the decision was overturned after linesman Ivan Nunez caught a replay of the incident on a cameraman .
